title: SET_DISCORD_RICH_PRESENCE_ASSET_SMALL
content:
0xF61D04C4// SetDiscordRichPresenceAssetSmall
void SET_DISCORD_RICH_PRESENCE_ASSET_SMALL(char* assetName);Parameters:assetName: The name of a valid asset registered on Discordapp's developer dashboard. Note that the asset has to be registered under the same discord API application set using the SET_DISCORD_APP_ID native.This native sets the small image asset for the discord rich presence implementation.
